  - src/infrastructure/di/container.ts (MODIFY) — Replace single ChatModelPort creation with ensemble wiring: factory.create() for each panel model → PanelRunner; factory.create() for judge model (if present) → JudgeStep; factory.create() for synthesizer → SynthesizeStep; pass all to RunFusionUseCase along with config/logger/clock. If judgeModel is null, create a JudgeStep with a no-op ChatModelPort stub that immediately returns.
  - src/infrastructure/di/container.test.ts (MODIFY) — Add tests: container resolves with anthropic providers in config, ensemble wiring does not throw, all config paths exercised (panel array, optional judge, synthesizer required), factory correctly routes openai and anthropic ModelRef instances.
